      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it's a good start. i think my students will also need to address the moral or ethical arguments that usually pop up from the other side. could you expand on the ethical case for strict enforcement? like, what's the principled argument for why a country has a moral right or even a duty to strictly limit who comes in?",
